    "We understand that pet owners love their animals and want the very best for them. There is a certain rapport that pet owners strive to reach with their vets and their pet groomers. They want to know that their dog or cat is in excellent hands when their ‘baby’ is dropped off for a grooming even if only for a couple of hours. Our professional dog groomer, Rogeria Santana ,instills that sense of trust in her customers. Loving and Care Pet Grooming is excited to have Rogeria Santana on board.This allows pet owners to take advantage of her 24 years experience. You’ll experience firsthand the love and passion she has for each and every pet and for the skills she has acquired to be the best at what she does.� Request a dog grooming today by calling: 914-619-6949",
